<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to Furniro</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body style="background-color: #FFF3E3; font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; padding: 30px;">
    <div class="container bg-white rounded p-4 shadow-sm">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="Furniro Logo" style="width: 120px;" />
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-warning">Welcome, <%= userName %>!</h2>

      <p>Thank you for registering with <strong>Furniro</strong>. We're excited to have you join our family!</p>

      <p>Explore our wide range of elegant furniture and design your dream space today.</p>

      <div class="text-center my-4">
        <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>" class="btn btn-warning text-white fw-semibold px-4 py-2">
          Start Shopping
        </a>
      </div>

      <p>If you need any help, feel free to contact our support team anytime.</p>

      <p class="mt-4">Best regards,<br />The Furniro Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
